ase in testosterone and glucocorticoid hormones measured during the breeding season. These three behaviors could potentially be used as early indicators to signal the onset of the breeding season and allow time to implement ex situ management changes to reduce the incidence of agonism between individuals.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Freeman, Hani D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wood, Michelle", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schook, Mandi W.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Leighty, Katherine A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lavin, Shana R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wiebe, Susan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Blowers, Tracy E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Daneault, Rachel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mylniczenko, Natalie", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wheaton, Catharine J.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/54f9f01225393c6abfab258366cbd118", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/f3c8b0729eaba0af9313ee451e3903476b1403d66e24a2ee504786e35fce1b98", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/7II4PKHR", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/7II4PKHR", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/155a697f6adbf89f979926fbaf3dcc50!/b209226-211692", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/26f7ce5dd404e33c6570edd4ba250d20", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article"